    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The engine has a noticeable knock and struggles to maintain idle, while the transmission shifts roughly between gears. Cosmetically, there is extensive rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells, along with multiple large dents and peeling clear coat. The interior shows heavy wear, including several tears in the upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This is a project car or a candidate for parts, sold strictly as-is.",
      "price": 4500.0,
