    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, which exemplifies a harmonious balance of performance and aesthetic integrity. The exterior retains a professional finish, while the cabin reflects a history of careful stewardship and consistent upkeep. Rigorously inspected to ensure mechanical excellence, this model offers a refined driving experience and stands as a premier choice for the discerning buyer seeking both value and distinction. This vehicle represents a secure investment in enduring quality.",
      "price": 36800.0,
